an (film)|Delivery Man]]'' (2013)\n| ''[[Starbuck (film)|Starbuck]]'' (2011, Canada)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Diabolique (1996 film)|Diabolique]]'' (1996)\n| ''[[Les Diaboliques (film)|Les Diaboliques]]'' (1955)\n| The novel ''Celle qui n'\u00e9tait plus'' ([[Boileau-Narcejac]])\n|-\n| ''[[Dinner for Schmucks]]'' (2010)\n| ''[[The Dinner Game|Le D\u00eener de Cons]]'' (1998)\n| The play ''[[Le D\u00eener de Cons]]'' ([[Francis Veber]])\n|-\n| ''[[Down and Out in Beverly Hills]]'' (1986)\n| ''[[Boudu sauv\u00e9 des eaux]]'' (1932)\n| The play ''Boudu sauv\u00e9 des eaux'' ([[Ren\u00e9 Fauchois]])\n|-\n| ''[[Dressed to Thrill]]'' (1935)\n| ''[[La couturi\u00e8re de Lun\u00e9ville]]'' (1932)\n| The play ''La Couturi\u00e8re de Lun\u00e9ville'' ([[Alfred Savoir]])\n|-\n| ''[[EDtv]]'' (1999)\n| ''[[Louis 19, King of the Airwaves|Louis 19, le roi des ondes]]'' (1994, Canada)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Eye of the Beholder (film)|Eye of the Beholder]]'' (1999)\n| ''[[Deadly Circuit|Mortelle Randonn\u00e9e]]'' (1983)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Fanny (1961 film)|Fanny]]'' (1961)\n| ''[[Marius (1931 film)|Marius]]'' (1929)<br>''[[Fanny (1932 film)|Fanny]]'' (1932)<br>''[[C\u00e9sar (film)|C\u00e9sar]]'' (1936)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Fant\u00f4mas (1920 serial)|Fant\u00f4mas]]'' (serial, 1920)\n| ''[[Fant\u00f4mas (1913 serial)|Fant\u00f4mas]]'' (serial, 1913)\n| The ''[[Fant\u00f4mas]]'' novels ([[Marcel Allain]], [[Pierre Souvestre]])\n|-\n| ''[[Fathers' Day (1997 film)|Fathers' Day]]'' (1997)\n| ''[[Les Comp\u00e8res]]'' (1983)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Firebird (1934 film)|The Firebird]]'' (1934)\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|Cette nuit-l\u00e0|fr|3=Cette nuit-l\u00e0 (film, 1933)|lt=Cette nuit-l\u00e0}}'' (1933)\n| The play ''Firebird'' ([[Lajos Zilahy]])\n|-\n| ''[[The First Offence]]'' (1936)\n| ''[[Mauvaise Graine]]'' (1934)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Flame and the Flesh]]'' (1954)\n| ''Naples au baiser de feu'' (1937)\n| The novel ''Naples au baiser de feu'' (Auguste Bailly)\n|-\n| ''[[Forty Little Mothers]]'' (1940)\n| ''[[Le mioche]]'' (1936)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Good Thief (film)|The Good Thief]]'' (2002)\n| ''[[Bob le flambeur]]'' (1956)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Grand Seduction]]'' (2013)\n| ''[[Seducing Doctor Lewis]]'' (2003, Canada)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[The Gunman (2015 film)|The Gunman]]'' (2015)\n| ''[[Le choc]]'' (1982)\n| The novel ''The Prone Gunman'' ([[Jean-Patrick Manchette]])\n|-\n| ''[[The Guv'nor (film)|The Guv'nor]]'' (1935)\n| ''Rothchild'' (1933)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Gypsy Melody]]'' (1936)\n| ''[[Juanita (1935 film)|Juanita]]'' (1935)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Happy New Year (1987 film)|Happy New Year]]'' (1987)\n| ''[[La bonne ann\u00e9e]]'' (1973)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Heartbeat (1946 film)|Heartbeat]]'' (1946)\n| ''[[Beating Heart (film)|Battement de coeur]]'' (1940)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Hell's Cargo]]'' (1939)\n| ''[[Alerte en M\u00e9diterran\u00e9e]]'' (1938)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Human Desire]]'' (1954)\n| ''[[La B\u00eate Humaine (film)|La B\u00eate Humaine]]'' (1938)\n| The novel ''[[La B\u00eate humaine]]'' ([[\u00c9mile Zola]])\n|-\n| ''[[Intersection (1994 film)|Intersection]]'' (1994)\n| ''[[Les choses de la vie]]'' (1970)\n| The novel ''Les choses de la vie'' ([[Paul Guimard]])\n|-\n| ''[[I Think I Love My Wife]]'' (2007)\n| ''[[Love in the Afternoon (1972 film)|L'Amour l'apr\u00e8s-midi]]'' (1972)\n|\n|-\n| ''[[I Was an Adventuress]]'' (1940)\n| ''{{Interlanguage link multi|J'\u00e9tais une aventuri\u00e8re|fr}}'' (1938)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Journal of a Crime]]'' (1934)\n| ''Une vie perdue'' (1933)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Jungle 2 Jungle]]'' (1997)\n| ''[[Un indien dans la ville]]'' (1994)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Just My Luck (1933 film)|Just My Luck]]'' (1933)\n| ''Aza\u00efs'' (1932)\n| The play ''Aza\u00efs ([[Fifty-Fifty (play)|Fifty-Fifty]])''\n|-\n| ''[[Just Visiting (film)|Just Visiting]]'' (2001)\n| ''[[Les Visiteurs]]'' (1993)\n| \n|-\n| ''[[A Kind of Murder]]'' (2016)\n| ''[[Enough Rope (film)|Le Meurtrier]]'' (1963)\n| The novel ''[[The Blunderer]]'' ([[Patricia Highsmith]])\n|-\n| ''[[The Lady in Question]] '' (1940)\n